Package nl.rug.nc.bicycleclient

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Callbackable<T>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckBikeFragment
    This subclass of Fragment provides the user interface where the users can check the parking time of a bicycle in a certain slot of a certain bicycle stand.
    HomeFragment
    This subclass of Fragment provides a home screen interface that contains buttons to the parking time checker and the reservation interface.
    MainActivity
    This is a top level interface that provides the App-wide navigation bar and contains the Home, Parking time checker and Reservation Fragments.
    ReserveSpotFragment
    This subclass of Fragment provides the user interface where the users can choose a bicycle stand and a slot number and reserve that slot if it is empty.
